Example Use Case
Add the following employees to trigger some alerts:

Name	Bank Account	Address	Hours Worked	Hourly Rate
Alice	123-456	10 Fleet St	85	9.50
Bob	123-456	10 Fleet St	40	11.00
Carol	999-888	10 Fleet St	42	12.00

FairFlag will detect:

Shared bank account between Alice and Bob

Shared address among Alice, Bob, and Carol

Aliceâ€™s excessive hours and underpaid wage

